# Requirements Analysis Document  
Application: TutorialNinja Demo E-Commerce  
URL: http://www.tutorialsninja.com/demo/

## 1. Business Requirements
- Provide a platform for users to browse, search, and purchase products online.
- Allow users to register, log in, and manage their account details.
- Enable complete shopping cart and checkout functionality.

## 2. Functional Requirements

### 2.1 User Management
- Register new users.
- Login/Logout.
- Forgotten password workflow.
- Modify account details.

### 2.2 Product Catalog
- Browse categories.
- Search products.
- View product details (images, description, price).
- Compare products.
- Wishlist functionality.

### 2.3 Cart & Checkout
- Add/update/remove products from cart.
- Apply coupons (if available).
- Checkout → Billing → Shipping → Payment.
- Guest checkout (if supported).

### 2.4 Order Management
- Order confirmation page.
- Order history for logged-in users.

## 3. Non-Functional Requirements
- Page loads under 3 seconds.
- Works on Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari.
- Basic security requirements.
- User-friendly UI and consistent navigation.

## 4. Assumptions & Dependencies
- Stable internet connection.
- Browsers allow JavaScript and cookies.
- No backend DB validation is in scope.
